                <p class="text-gray-600">Estados, fechas, y datos presentados de forma consistente y fácil de auditar.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-sky-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
